espa.com/cinco-ranch/facials/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://katymedtechspa.com/blogs/news/experience-the-best-facial-in-san-antonio-at-katy-medictech-spa?srsltid=AfmBOoqq3u7JHVUz4RA6DPwcgnv8h7wb3MWA1La3A5HCqBPG5lqliRHI"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.avivaderm.com/katy/"}]}},{"id":"tco_9630819b-efc1-9df9-b691-5ccf3328f438_call-d18579c6-a2de-4247-8e32-ea40092c89a9-6","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_9630819b-efc1-9df9-b691-5ccf3328f438_call-d18579c6-a2de-4247-8e32-ea40092c89a9-7","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**Anita’s Skin Care Clinic and Facials by Jada stand out as top options for acne-focused facial treatments in Katy, TX, based on specialization, certifications, and client feedback.**[[1]](https://anitasskincareclinickaty.com/)[[2]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n### Top Recommendations\nHere are the strongest options, prioritized by acne-specific expertise:\n\n- **Anita’s Skin Care Clinic** (Highly recommended for acne)  \n  This clinic specializes in holistic skincare with dedicated acne programs. It is a certified DMK skin revision clinic and an acne-certified clinic with Face Reality. Services include custom facials, an Acne Bootcamp Program, acne detox facials with blue light therapy, chemical peels, and more. Clients report significant improvement in cystic acne and clearer skin after sessions. Holistic approach addresses underlying causes.  \n  **Location**: 22167 Westheimer Pkwy #130, Katy, TX 77450.  \n  **Contact**: (713) 515-8522 or book via Vagaro.  \n  Strong reviews praise the knowledgeable esthetician and visible results.[[3]](https://www.vagaro.com/anitasskincare)[[3]](https://www.vagaro.com/anitasskincare)\n\n- **Facials by Jada** (Excellent ratings and targeted acne facials)  \n  Jada O’Neill offers personalized, results-driven treatments with over 20 years of experience. Key option: the “Clear Skin Purify” facial (detoxifying/decongesting with extractions, clay mask, and optional oxygen therapy) designed for acne-prone skin. Other relevant services include dermaplaning (helps with acne scars) and various glow facials. Clients highlight calming studio, expertise, and improved skin after treatments. High Yelp rating (around 4.8/5).  \n  **Location**: 815 Merlin Roost Court, Katy, TX.  \n  **Contact**: 832-724-8445 or book online.[[4]](https://www.yelp.com/biz/facials-by-jada-katy)[[5]](https://facialsbyjada.com/)\n\n- **Other strong mentions**:\n  - **Spavia Cinco Ranch** — Offers a clarifying deep-cleansing acne facial with Mangosteen extract for detoxifying and renewing acne-prone skin.[[6]](https://cincoranchtx.spaviadayspa.com/skin-care)\n  - **Hibiscus Aesthetics** — Personalized acne treatments using tailored products to control oiliness and breakouts.[[7]](https://www.hibiscus.health/facial-treatments/acne-treatment/)\n  - **MedSpa at Villagio** or **Katy Med Tech Spa** — Award-winning or luxury med spas with various facials and skincare options.[[8]](https://medspaatvillagio.com/)\n\n### Tips for Choosing and Booking\n- **For severe or persistent acne**, consider a consultation with a dermatologist (e.g., AVIVA Dermatology or Clear Dermatology in the area) alongside esthetician treatments, as medical-grade options like prescription topicals or lasers may complement facials.[[9]](https://www.avivaderm.com/katy/)\n- Check current reviews on Yelp or Google, as ratings can shift. Many places offer consultations to customize treatments.\n- Factors like extractions, chemical peels, LED/blue light, or oxygen therapy are commonly effective for acne facials.\n- Book ahead and confirm availability, as these are popular local spots.\n\nFor the latest details or to compare packages, visit the providers’ websites or call directly. Results vary by skin type, so a personalized assessment is ideal.","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://anitasskincareclinickaty.com/","start_index":183,"end_index":227,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":227,"end_index":298,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.vagaro.com/anitasskincare","start_index":1081,"end_index":1125,"title":"3"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.vagaro.com/anitasskincare","start_index":1125,"end_index":1169,"title":"3"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/facials-by-jada-katy","start_index":1800,"end_index":1852,"title":"4"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://facialsbyjada.com/","start_index":1852,"end_index":1885,"title":"5"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://cincoranchtx.spaviadayspa.com/skin-care","start_index":2061,"end_index":2115,"title":"6"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.hibiscus.health/facial-treatments/acne-treatment/","start_index":2233,"end_index":2301,"title":"7"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://medspaatvillagio.com/","start_index":2431,"end_index":2467,"title":"8"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.avivaderm.com/katy/","start_index":2763,"end_index":2801,"title":"9"}]}],"id":"msg_9630819b-efc1-9df9-b691-5ccf3328f438","role":"assistant","type":"message","status":"completed"}],"parallel_tool_calls":true,"previous_response_id":null,"reasoning":{"effort":"low","summary":"detailed"},"temperature":0.7,"text":{"format":{"type":"text"}},"tool_choice":"auto","tools":[{"type":"web_search","search_context_size":"medium"}],"top_p":0.95,"usage":{"input_tokens":27520,"input_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":15616},"output_tokens":1608,"output_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":889},"total_tokens":29128,"num_sources_used":0,"num_server_side_tools_used":8,"cost_in_usd_ticks":620232000,"server_side_tool_usage_details":{"web_search_calls":8,"x_search_calls":0,"code_interpreter_calls":0,"file_search_calls":0,"mcp_calls":0,"document_search_calls":0},"context_details":{"input_tokens":12825,"output_tok